 CR-driven instabilities generated near radio\nbubbles may also play an important role redistributing AGN energy throughout\nclusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Jul 2022 18:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-22"}
