or numerical examples that are performed for the breakup of long liquid\nfilaments and show qualitatively different phenomena in different scaling\nregimes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jul 2022 04:39:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 11:53:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
