better performance than planning with\na separate trained prediction module in both open-loop and closed-loop tests.\nMoreover, the ablation study indicates that the learnable components in the\nframework are essential to ensure planning stability and performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jul 2022 11:38:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Feb 2023 06:37:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-21"}
